GME"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"你咁醒你咪講囉"},{"pid":"a56fb58ce0b23fc32b71a14bd5cef71efed2d040","tid":2382433,"uid":9576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:26:38.000Z","msg":"集中火力沖上1000 啦 轉你老母咩"},{"pid":"cdd4432139640679705e8f23f5fe1b3fc2c4c7e7","tid":2382433,"uid":172733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c60e9ce9d23e29794a511cf4996fd844038a5b2","tid":2382433,"uid":76845,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"GME 超過100%沽空喎<br />\n依隻憑乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"呃你錢過去"},{"pid":"bd22aa3d816b7cb69395447c2ad5de349ad57932","tid":2382433,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"支牛post 大陸人寫 唔cap圖po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世紀逼空大戰正在上演&mdash;&mdash;$游戲驛站(<a href=\"http://GME.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGME.US&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=f107190a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://GME.US</a>)$是近期美股市場最為引人注目的股票，這場大戲裏不僅有WallstreetBets（WSB）論壇抱團做多的美國散户，還有$特斯拉(<a href=\"http://TSLA.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTSLA.US&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=8e2d1e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://TSLA.US</a>)$創始人馬斯克，有「大空頭」之稱的Michael Burry，做空機構香櫞，當然還有據傳已經被逼空至破產的曾經千億人民幣規模的對衝基金Melvin。<br />\n<br />\n而就在昨天，維珍銀河大股東、Social Capital創始人Chamath Palihapitiya也加入了進來。<br />\n<br />\n1月26日，Chamath發佈推特詢問應該買入什麼，準備拿小10萬出來玩玩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3quiL5t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3quiL5t.png&h=c7bcdb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這條推特下方，目前最熱門的回帖即是一名網友在推薦遊戲驛站。隨後，Chamath表示被説服了，還貼出交易截圖，買入遊戲驛站2月19日到期的Call 50張，行權價為115美元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bO2gxLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbO2gxLy.png&h=30b72738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而在一眾大佬的加持下，遊戲驛站週二收盤價已達147美元，盤後更是狂飆41%，股價衝到209美元。週三盤前一度飆漲至90%，波動劇烈，目前股價為280美元，今年以來已經翻了十幾倍。<br />\n<br />\nChamath大舉做多遊戲驛站，還有另外一重好處，他持股4.73%的$Virgin Galactic Holdings Inc(<a href=\"http://SPCE.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FSPCE.US&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=fdd692d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://SPCE.US</a>)$維珍銀河週二飆漲16%，一舉創下歷史新高。週三盤前也大漲11%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRd3Xcj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRd3Xcj.png&h=77a4f351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而維珍銀河與遊戲驛站的聯繫在於，這兩家公司都被大量做空。據highshortinterest網站的數據，目前遊戲驛站位居被做空股票的榜首，而維珍銀河緊隨其後。近期，在WallstreetBets（WSB）論壇被熱烈討論的AMC位列第三。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JDTjvxn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJDTjvxn.png&h=3ed2e3c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n並且，維珍銀河近期還獲得女股神的加持，凱西&middot;伍德(Cathie Wood)正將目光投向太空探索行業。<br />\n<br />\n1月13日，由伍德擔任CEO的方舟投資管理公司(ARK Investment Management)提交申請，計劃推出一隻名為ARK太空探索的ETF，交易代碼為ARKX。儘管這隻基金還沒有上市，具體持股情況也不得而知，但這一消息已經帶動許多和太空業務有關的公司股價上漲，這其中就包括SPCE。<br />\n<br />\n仍然在SPCE堅守的空頭們，準備好迎接洶湧如潮的美股散户了嗎？"},{"pid":"eda6324221e797a5262d97471abff6505e1595e8","tid":2382433,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:33:18.000Z","msg":"跟"},{"pid":"11a090ead8f33d8258e221d191f6c19ad9cca3d7","tid":2382433,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:33:47.000Z","msg":"呢隻咩事"},{"pid":"0317e779603d560e9ce611fa9da18bc57f42b67c","tid":2382433,"uid":131884,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"7203c3e9ccc6d538549d85f5ce6dc377c6b1ab17","tid":2382433,"uid":149096,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"491aca0793d9d664ae18d28e1f143753cd3b3793","tid":2382433,"uid":131884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"轉你老母閪咩...<br />\n大家到底明唔明點解要入GME"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"你咁醒你咪講囉"},"ci